        <mxCell id="44" value="&lt;b&gt;Each Subagent:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. bmpipe run --story {id}&lt;br&gt;   --stop-after review&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;2. Report findings JSON&lt;br&gt;   to orchestrator&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;3. [on SendMessage]&lt;br&gt;   Apply patches, re-test&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;4. [on SendMessage]&lt;br&gt;   bmpipe --resume-from trace&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;5. Report gate decision" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=10;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" parent="1" vertex="1">
